{"tid":306082,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"直播從零開始的機戰v之路Day2 到晚上轉玩steam特價遊戲 4:35開始","createTime":"2017-07-02T08:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T10:40:21.000Z","uid":84544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7463dd38cd84a0fb00074430428875f63dfd4d8","tid":306082,"uid":84544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"《超級機器人大戰》系列集結眾多動畫作品中登場的機器人，是一款超越作品藩籬並肩戰鬥的戰略模擬 RPG。本作嶄新的世界觀與全一部完結的劇情，讓從未體驗過《超級機器人大戰》系列的玩家也非常適合嘗試。掌握本作關鍵的男、女主角皆為原創角色，玩家將選擇其一進行遊戲，而未被選擇的一方則將以輔佐身分加入。<br />\n<br />\n　　而如《勇者特急隊》、《宇宙戰艦大和號 2199)》、《Cross Ange ～天使與龍的輪舞～》等著名的作品都將首次於《超級機器人大戰》系列登場。此外，為了迎接《超級機器人大戰》25 周年，本作亦特別設計多款原創機體及角色於遊戲內參戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/70/0001385570.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F70%2F0001385570.JPG&h=2c83712b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/67/0001385567.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F67%2F0001385567.JPG&h=1e64dc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/iamkwankwan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fiamkwankwan&d=NY3EFI70W6kEmCqZ3TJJGk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d1681552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/iamkwankwan</a><br />\nYoutube 重溫: <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA&d=NY3EFI70W6kEmCqZ3TJJGk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3f1d991d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA</a><br />\n到晚上轉玩steam特價遊戲 歡迎跟隨"},{"pid":"c8ebecb1480783b570b3024320c7ea95ed281bad","tid":306082,"uid":84544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{